[
  {
    "startTime": 6.88,
    "endTime": 9.24,
    "text": "Hello. This is 6 Minute English from"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 9.24,
    "endTime": 11.06,
    "text": "BBC Learning English. I'm Neil."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 11.06,
    "endTime": 12.26,
    "text": "And I'm Sam."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 12.26,
    "endTime": 14.5,
    "text": "Do you cry easily, Sam? I mean, when"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 14.5,
    "endTime": 16.26,
    "text": "was the last time you cried?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 16.26,
    "endTime": 18.540000000000003,
    "text": "Let me think... Last week watching"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 18.558,
    "endTime": 20.823,
    "text": "a movie, probably. I was watching"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 20.823,
    "endTime": 21.990000000000002,
    "text": "a really dramatic"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 21.99,
    "endTime": 24.485,
    "text": "film and in one scene, the heroine"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 24.485,
    "endTime": 26.72,
    "text": "gets separated from her children."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 26.72,
    "endTime": 28.74,
    "text": "I just burst out crying."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 28.74,
    "endTime": 30.299999999999997,
    "text": "How about you Neil - when was"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 30.3,
    "endTime": 31.96,
    "text": "he last time you cried?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 31.96,
    "endTime": 34.480000000000004,
    "text": "Men don't cry, Sam."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 34.48,
    "endTime": 37.019999999999996,
    "text": "Come on, Neil! That's a bit stereotypical,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 37.02,
    "endTime": 38.615,
    "text": "isn't it? - the idea that men"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 38.615,
    "endTime": 39.5,
    "text": "don't show their"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 39.5,
    "endTime": 42.86,
    "text": "emotions and women cry all the time."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 42.86,
    "endTime": 45.08,
    "text": "Well, that's an interesting point, Sam,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 45.08,
    "endTime": 46.839999999999996,
    "text": "because in today's programme"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 46.84,
    "endTime": 48.52,
    "text": "we're discussing crying."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 48.52,
    "endTime": 50.374,
    "text": "We'll be investigating the reasons why"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 50.374,
    "endTime": 51.672000000000004,
    "text": "we cry and looking at some"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 51.672,
    "endTime": 52.57,
    "text": "of the differences"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 52.57,
    "endTime": 54.079,
    "text": "between men and women and"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 54.079,
    "endTime": 55.797,
    "text": "between crying in public and"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 55.797,
    "endTime": 57.760999999999996,
    "text": "in private. And of course, we'll"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 57.761,
    "endTime": 59.817,
    "text": "be learning some related vocabulary"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 59.817,
    "endTime": 60.64,
    "text": "along the way."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 60.64,
    "endTime": 63.256,
    "text": "I guess it's kind of true that women"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 63.256,
    "endTime": 65.333,
    "text": "do cry more than men. People"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 65.333,
    "endTime": 66.89,
    "text": "often think crying is"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 66.89,
    "endTime": 69.383,
    "text": "only about painful feelings but we also"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 69.383,
    "endTime": 71.145,
    "text": "cry to show joy and when we"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 71.145,
    "endTime": 72.58,
    "text": "are moved by something"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 72.58,
    "endTime": 75.44,
    "text": "beautiful like music or a painting."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 75.44,
    "endTime": 77.711,
    "text": "So, maybe women are just more in touch"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 77.72,
    "endTime": 79.06,
    "text": "with their feelings and that's"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 79.06,
    "endTime": 80.64,
    "text": "why they cry more."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 80.64,
    "endTime": 82.64,
    "text": "Well actually, Sam, that brings me"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 82.64,
    "endTime": 85.1,
    "text": "to our quiz question. According to"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 85.1,
    "endTime": 86.55999999999999,
    "text": "a study from 2017"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 86.56,
    "endTime": 89.26,
    "text": "conducted in the UK, on average, how"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 89.26,
    "endTime": 91.84,
    "text": "many times a year do women cry? Is it:"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 91.84,
    "endTime": 96.04,
    "text": "a) 52, b) 72, or c) 102?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 96.04,
    "endTime": 98.80000000000001,
    "text": "Hmm, it's a tricky question, Neil."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 98.8,
    "endTime": 100.64,
    "text": "I mean, there are so many different"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 100.649,
    "endTime": 102.1,
    "text": "reasons why people"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 102.1,
    "endTime": 104.88,
    "text": "cry. And what makes me cry might make"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 104.88,
    "endTime": 107.24,
    "text": "someone else laugh. I think"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 107.247,
    "endTime": 109.28,
    "text": "some of my female friends"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 109.28,
    "endTime": 112.371,
    "text": "probably cry around once a week, so I'll"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 112.371,
    "endTime": 114.38,
    "text": "guess the answer is a) 52."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 114.38,
    "endTime": 117.095,
    "text": "OK, Sam. We'll find out later if you were"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 117.095,
    "endTime": 119.81,
    "text": "right. Now, while it may be true that men"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 119.81,
    "endTime": 123.262,
    "text": "cry less often, it also seems that they feel"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 123.262,
    "endTime": 126.22,
    "text": "less embarrassed about crying in public."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 126.22,
    "endTime": 128.72,
    "text": "This may be because of differences in"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 128.72,
    "endTime": 130.34,
    "text": "how men and women think"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 130.344,
    "endTime": 131.79999999999998,
    "text": "others will view their"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 131.81,
    "endTime": 134.649,
    "text": "public displays of emotion. Here's BBC"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 134.649,
    "endTime": 137.011,
    "text": "Radio 4's Woman's Hour speaking"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 137.02,
    "endTime": 138.459,
    "text": "to therapist Joanna"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 138.46,
    "endTime": 141.92000000000002,
    "text": "Cross about the issue of crying at work."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 144.18,
    "endTime": 146.12,
    "text": "Let's take the workplace. If you've got"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 146.12,
    "endTime": 148.44,
    "text": "somebody who seems to cry regularly,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 148.44,
    "endTime": 149.38,
    "text": "I think that's"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 149.38,
    "endTime": 152.0,
    "text": "not helpful for the individual because then"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 152.015,
    "endTime": 154.51899999999998,
    "text": "if they cry over something that really is"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 154.52,
    "endTime": 156.14000000000001,
    "text": "important to them, they might not be"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 156.14,
    "endTime": 157.48,
    "text": "taken so seriously - or they"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 157.48,
    "endTime": 158.94,
    "text": "get a label. But I"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 158.94,
    "endTime": 161.24,
    "text": "do think crying is often a build-up of"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 161.259,
    "endTime": 162.992,
    "text": "frustration and undealt-with"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 162.992,
    "endTime": 164.54,
    "text": "situations and it's a bit"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 164.54,
    "endTime": 166.45999999999998,
    "text": "of a final straw moment."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 167.84,
    "endTime": 170.31900000000002,
    "text": "So people who regularly cry at work"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 170.319,
    "endTime": 172.685,
    "text": "risk not being taken seriously - not"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 172.685,
    "endTime": 173.54,
    "text": "being treated"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 173.54,
    "endTime": 176.07899999999998,
    "text": "as deserving attention or respect."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 176.079,
    "endTime": 178.531,
    "text": "And they might even get a label - become"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 178.531,
    "endTime": 180.594,
    "text": "thought of as having a particular"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 180.594,
    "endTime": 181.719,
    "text": "character, whether"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 181.72,
    "endTime": 183.66,
    "text": "that's true or not."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 183.66,
    "endTime": 186.12,
    "text": "Here's Joanna Cross again:"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 186.72,
    "endTime": 188.94,
    "text": "You build up your resentments, your"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 188.94,
    "endTime": 190.78,
    "text": "lack of boundaries, not being able"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 190.78,
    "endTime": 192.02,
    "text": "to say 'no' and"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 192.02,
    "endTime": 193.20000000000002,
    "text": "then somebody says, 'Can you go and"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 193.205,
    "endTime": 194.139,
    "text": "make a cup of tea?' and you"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 194.139,
    "endTime": 194.9,
    "text": "suddenly find yourself"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 194.9,
    "endTime": 196.52,
    "text": "weeping. And everybody says,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 196.52,
    "endTime": 199.26000000000002,
    "text": "'What's wrong with her?', you know, but actually"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 199.27,
    "endTime": 200.76000000000002,
    "text": "that's often a backlog"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 200.76,
    "endTime": 202.82,
    "text": "of situations."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 204.44,
    "endTime": 206.88,
    "text": "So, a common reason for crying at work"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 206.88,
    "endTime": 208.9,
    "text": "seems to be a build-up"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 208.9,
    "endTime": 210.54,
    "text": "of resentments - feelings"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 210.549,
    "endTime": 212.338,
    "text": "of anger when you think you have been"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 212.338,
    "endTime": 213.858,
    "text": "treated unfairly or have been"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 213.858,
    "endTime": 215.22,
    "text": "forced to accept something"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 215.22,
    "endTime": 216.59,
    "text": "you don't like."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 216.59,
    "endTime": 218.36,
    "text": "When left undealt with, these feelings"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 218.36,
    "endTime": 221.06,
    "text": "can create a backlog - an accumulation"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 221.06,
    "endTime": 222.48,
    "text": "of issues that you"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 222.48,
    "endTime": 225.51999999999998,
    "text": "should have dealt with before but didn't."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 225.529,
    "endTime": 227.577,
    "text": "Right. And then, like Joanna says,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 227.577,
    "endTime": 229.541,
    "text": "someone asks you to do something"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 229.541,
    "endTime": 230.82999999999998,
    "text": "very simple and easy,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 230.83,
    "endTime": 232.94500000000002,
    "text": "like make a cup of tea, and you start"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 232.945,
    "endTime": 234.88899999999998,
    "text": "weeping - another word for crying."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 234.889,
    "endTime": 237.50300000000001,
    "text": "That's a good example of a final straw"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 237.503,
    "endTime": 239.326,
    "text": "moment, a term which comes"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 239.326,
    "endTime": 241.07899999999998,
    "text": "from the expression, 'The"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 241.079,
    "endTime": 243.549,
    "text": "straw that broke the camel's back'."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 243.549,
    "endTime": 245.06,
    "text": "The final straw means"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 245.06,
    "endTime": 247.219,
    "text": "a further problem which itself"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 247.219,
    "endTime": 249.82,
    "text": "might be insignificant but which finally"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 249.82,
    "endTime": 251.51,
    "text": "makes you want to give up."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 251.51,
    "endTime": 253.119,
    "text": "I hope this programme won't be"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 253.119,
    "endTime": 254.62,
    "text": "the final straw for us, Sam."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 254.62,
    "endTime": 257.358,
    "text": "I doubt it, Neil. The only time I cry at work"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 257.358,
    "endTime": 259.096,
    "text": "is when you used to bring in"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 259.096,
    "endTime": 260.4,
    "text": "your onion sandwiches"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 260.4,
    "endTime": 263.746,
    "text": "for lunch. In fact, I can feel a tear rolling"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 263.746,
    "endTime": 265.68,
    "text": "down my cheek right now..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 265.68,
    "endTime": 268.07,
    "text": "Ah, so that counts as one of your cries,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 268.07,
    "endTime": 269.658,
    "text": "Sam. Remember, I asked you"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 269.658,
    "endTime": 270.819,
    "text": "on average how many"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 270.819,
    "endTime": 272.899,
    "text": "times a year women in the UK"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 272.899,
    "endTime": 274.31,
    "text": "cry - and you said?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 274.31,
    "endTime": 276.4,
    "text": "I said a) 52."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 276.4,
    "endTime": 278.979,
    "text": "Well, don't cry when I tell you that you"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 278.98,
    "endTime": 280.889,
    "text": "were wrong. The actual answer"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 280.889,
    "endTime": 282.6,
    "text": "was c) 72 times a year."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 282.6,
    "endTime": 285.12,
    "text": "Which on average is more than men,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 285.14,
    "endTime": 287.75399999999996,
    "text": "but less than parents of new-born babies,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 287.754,
    "endTime": 288.52000000000004,
    "text": "both mothers"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 288.52,
    "endTime": 291.255,
    "text": "and fathers. They cry almost as much"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 291.255,
    "endTime": 292.46999999999997,
    "text": "as their babies!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 292.47,
    "endTime": 294.90000000000003,
    "text": "Today, we've been talking about crying - or"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 294.9,
    "endTime": 297.2,
    "text": "weeping, as it's sometimes called."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 297.2,
    "endTime": 299.97999999999996,
    "text": "People who often cry at work risk not"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 299.99,
    "endTime": 302.38,
    "text": "being taken seriously - not treated"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 302.395,
    "endTime": 303.21999999999997,
    "text": "as deserving"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 303.22,
    "endTime": 305.56,
    "text": "of attention or respect."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 305.56,
    "endTime": 307.74,
    "text": "This means they might get a label -"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 307.746,
    "endTime": 309.34,
    "text": "becoming known as someone with"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 309.344,
    "endTime": 310.409,
    "text": "a particular kind of"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 310.409,
    "endTime": 312.42,
    "text": "personality, even though that"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 312.44,
    "endTime": 313.76,
    "text": "may not be true."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 313.76,
    "endTime": 315.88,
    "text": "But crying is also a healthy way of"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 315.886,
    "endTime": 318.062,
    "text": "expressing emotions. It can help"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 318.062,
    "endTime": 319.49,
    "text": "deal with resentments"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 319.49,
    "endTime": 321.90000000000003,
    "text": "- feelings of anger that you have"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 321.9,
    "endTime": 324.08,
    "text": "been treated unfairly."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 324.08,
    "endTime": 325.71999999999997,
    "text": "If we don't deal with these feelings in"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 325.72,
    "endTime": 327.48,
    "text": "some way, they can grow into"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 327.48,
    "endTime": 329.46000000000004,
    "text": "a backlog - an accumulation"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 329.46,
    "endTime": 331.88,
    "text": "of unresolved issues that you now"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 331.88,
    "endTime": 333.38,
    "text": "need to deal with."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 333.38,
    "endTime": 335.26,
    "text": "And if you don't deal with them, you might"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 335.26,
    "endTime": 337.15999999999997,
    "text": "become a ticking bomb"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 337.16,
    "endTime": 338.62,
    "text": "waiting to explode."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 338.62,
    "endTime": 341.0,
    "text": "Then anything someone says to you can"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 341.0,
    "endTime": 342.7,
    "text": "become the final straw - the"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 342.7,
    "endTime": 344.44,
    "text": "last small problem which"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 344.44,
    "endTime": 346.2,
    "text": "makes you want to give up"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 346.2,
    "endTime": 347.65999999999997,
    "text": "and maybe start crying."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 349.82,
    "endTime": 351.32,
    "text": "What's the matter, Neil?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 351.32,
    "endTime": 353.2,
    "text": "Was it something I said?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 353.2,
    "endTime": 355.03999999999996,
    "text": "No, Sam - I'm crying because it's"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 355.052,
    "endTime": 356.75,
    "text": "the end of the programme!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 356.75,
    "endTime": 359.279,
    "text": "Ahh, don't worry because we'll be back"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 359.279,
    "endTime": 360.90999999999997,
    "text": "soon for another edition"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 360.91,
    "endTime": 362.54,
    "text": "of 6 Minute English. But"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 362.54,
    "endTime": 363.96000000000004,
    "text": "bye for now."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 363.96,
    "endTime": 364.88,
    "text": "Bye."
  }
]